[center][b][color=#feca57][size=6][u]Slide/Pump Locking Feature[/u]
[/size][/color][/b][color=#feca57]
[size=4]If you want the shotgun slide/pump to remain locked, simply Hold the Trigger/Spell-Menu button on the hand which is holding the pump. 

This should allow you to aim freely without accidentally pumping the shotgun again.[/size][/color][/center]
